                            et &agrave; la </span><a style="text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.google.com/privacy.html"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #008489; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Politique de confidentialit&eacute; de Google</span></a>
